{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If you had taken five minutes more, that would have been taken all the way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you would have had nothing to eat until tomorrow morning-- the black coffee, the black water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So this was our arrival in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were then, as I say, in that barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the next morning, we, we were assigned to work groups.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And again, there too, I was fortunate enough to be ordered into a, into a workshop, where they assigned my own guard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I marched and had my own guard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I felt like a big shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, the interesting thing is, this guard wasn't there to, to protect me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was guarding that I don't do anything bad, the most dangerous fellow that I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother and I fortunately were still together at that moment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were separated later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'll probably come to that somewhat later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our mother remained in, in, in Terezin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when-- what we heard from eyewitnesses, when she was becoming more and more desperate, she went to the officials and asked them, in her naivete-- and I, I mean this lovingly-- and asked them that she would be, that she, if she couldn't be sent to her sons.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After all, that's what a mother wants to do then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so of course, they were always welcoming volunteers that would be sent away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so therefore, she was put on train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From witnesses that were with her, we found out that she did the same train ride.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's, it's a miracle that she survived it, because by that time, she was a gravely ill woman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Number one, she had a very serious cancer surgery from which she had not yet recovered when she was, when we were incarcerated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was incarcerated.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
